<RoughNotation
                type="bracket"
                brackets={['left', 'right']}
                show={true}
                color="#FF0000"
                animationDelay={300}
                animationDuration={1800}
              >
I am a website developer, bot developer, graphic designer, and a bit of reverse engineer. I learned to make a website from 2020
I learned to use javascript in 2020, i'm also learn how to use Adobe software like Photoshop, After Effect at 2021. I'm currently learning <RoughNotation animationDelay="1000" animationDuration="1800" type="highlight" color="#0ea4e9" strokeWidth="3" show={true}>Cloud Computing.</RoughNotation>

</RoughNotation>

## üèÜ Achievements
- <RoughNotation type="highlight" color="#FF0000" show={true} animationDelay={500} animationDuration={1800}>Tahfidz Qur'an</RoughNotation> Juz 30
- Third place in the <RoughNotation type="highlight" color="#0a2585ff" show={true} animationDelay={500} animationDuration={1800}>VALORANT</RoughNotation> Tournament at GS Gaming Arena

## üî¨ Education
- Universitas Muhammadiyah Bengkulu
- SMKN 1 Kota Bengkulu
- SMPN 4 Kota Bengkulu
- MTs Ja-alHaq (School Transfer)

## üõ†Ô∏è Skills
- Programming (HTML, CSS, Javascript, PHP, Python)
- Graphic design (Photoshop, Figma, Alight Motion)
- Movie Editing (After Effect, Premiere Pro, CapCut)
- Competitive VALORANT (peak rank: Ascendant 3)

## ‚ù§Ô∏è Others
See all my projects on [Projects Page](/projects)


## ‚åõ Time Line

### 2024
- I Learn Cloud Computing
- I Learn [AWS](https://aws.amazon.com/) for the <RoughNotation type="highlight" color="#FF0000" show={true} animationDelay={500} animationDuration={1800}> first time.</RoughNotation>

### 2022

- I learn NEXTJS  <RoughNotation type="underline" show={true} color="#FBCFE8" animationDelay={1500} animationDuration={1800} multiline={true} >(Now) </RoughNotation>
- I created Nuevy (Bot Discord) DISCONTINUED

### 2021

- I experimented with reverse-engineering online games such as [ROBLOX](https://roblox.com/).
- My first WhatsApp bot (I forked [Nurutomo](https://github.com/Nurutomo/wabot-aq)'s Repository.)

### 2020

- I'm learning javascript for the first time.
- COVID-19.
- I create my first website using html and css.
- I learned my first HTML.

### 2019
- I join discord.

### 2018
- Graduate Tahfidz Quran.

### 2007

-  üë∂ Born and raised in Bengkulu, Indonesia üáÆüá©.
